					</p>

					<p class="text-lg text-warm-800 leading-relaxed mb-8">
						Whether you're dealing with trauma, anxiety, grief, or work-related stress, Brainspotting offers a powerful alternative to traditional talk therapy for Emeryville residents.
					</p>

					<div class="bg-primary-50 p-8 rounded-lg mb-8">
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">Why Emeryville Residents Choose Brainspotting</h3>
						<ul class="space-y-3">
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
								</svg>
								<span class="text-warm-800"><strong>Convenient location:</strong> Just 10 minutes from Emeryville via San Pablo Ave</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
								</svg>
								<span class="text-warm-800"><strong>Flexible options:</strong> In-person or telehealth sessions</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
