							<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">Tech Industry Burnout</h3>
							<p class="text-warm-700 mb-4">
								Emeryville tech workers dealing with burnout, imposter syndrome, and work stress find Brainspotting helps restore balance and creativity.
							</p>
							<a href="/anxiety" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">
								Learn about anxiety treatment →
							</a>
						</div>

						<div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">Trauma & PTSD</h3>
							<p class="text-warm-700 mb-4">
								Effective trauma processing for Emeryville residents seeking healing without having to relive traumatic experiences.
							</p>
							<a href="/trauma" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">
								Learn about trauma treatment →
							</a>
						</div>

						<div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">Performance Enhancement</h3>
							<p class="text-warm-700 mb-4">
								Emeryville professionals use Brainspotting to overcome creative blocks and enhance performance at work.
							</p>
