						<ul class="space-y-2 text-warm-700">
							<li>• <strong>By car:</strong> 10 minutes via San Pablo Ave or I-580</li>
							<li>• <strong>By AC Transit:</strong> Lines 72, 72M, 72R connect Emeryville to Grand Ave</li>
							<li>• <strong>By bike:</strong> Easy ride via bike lanes on San Pablo Ave</li>
							<li>• <strong>Parking:</strong> Street parking available on Grand Ave</li>
						</ul>

						<h4 class="font-bold text-primary-900 mb-2 mt-6">Emeryville Areas Served:</h4>
						<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-warm-700">
